title: Amar Akbar Anthony
subTitle: Three brothers, each raised in different religious households, reunite after many years in a chance encounter. They set out to take revenge on those responsible for separating them.

title: Fiffty Fiffty
subTitle: Abandoned by his parents, Kishan becomes an elusive robber and teams up with Mary. However, when she leaves him to pursue her grand plan, he decides to seek revenge from the man who ruined his life.

title: Dil
subTitle: A father pretends to be a rich industrialist to improve his son's chances of marrying in to wealth. However, his plan backfires on him when his true identity is found out.

title: Paayal
subTitle: A widowed woman's daughter elopes with her lover. Years later, when her granddaughter also falls in love, she strives to accept the relationship.

title: Khwahish
subTitle: Two individuals fall in love and marry against their parents' wishes. However, their life takes a dramatic turn when the woman is diagnosed with a life-threatening disease.

title: Kya Yehi Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Rahul falls in love with Sandhya, a fellow college student, but realises that she does not reciprocate his feelings. Undeterred by her rejection, he still pursues her but pays a huge price for it.

title: Neel Kamal
subTitle: Sita's sleepwalking turns out to be a cause of concern to her husband and family. When they investigate, they realize that her current behaviour is linked to her previous life.

title: Chalta Hai Yaar
subTitle: Frustrated with his wife, Namdev, a businessman, decides to end his life. However, things take a turn when he envisions his dead father who encourages him to rethink his decision.

title: Karle Pyaar Karle
subTitle: When childhood friends Kabir and Preet play a game that results in a crime, he and his mother leave town. They reunite after 12 years but Preet believes they must maintain distance.

title: Naina
subTitle: After years of blindness caused by an accident, Naina gets a successful cornea transplant. However, she soon begins to see terrifying visions that prompt her to investigate the source of her sight.

title: Ghulam-E-Musthafa
subTitle: A notorious hitman forsakes a life of crime after his lady love suffers a tragic death due to his professional rivalries. However, the mafia compels him to return for a final hit job.

title: Ghulam-E-Musthafa
subTitle: A notorious hitman forsakes a life of crime after his lady love suffers a tragic death due to his professional rivalries. However, the mafia compels him to return for a final hit job.

title: Champion
subTitle: Rajveer, a police officer, is tasked with protecting a nine-year-old heir, Abbas. However, the job gets complicated when Nazir, a dangerous criminal, seeks to harm the child.

title: Chaand Kaa Tukdaa
subTitle: NRI Shyam comes to India to fulfil the final wish of his late mother who wanted him to marry an Indian girl. Unbeknownst to him, the girl he falls in love with is a pawn in the hands of his enemies.

title: Pyar Hi Pyar
subTitle: At an orphanage, Kailashnath identifies Vijay as his biological son and takes him home. Years later, a man named Ashok arrives and claims to be Kailashnath's real son.

title: Mera Damad
subTitle: Jai's father asks him to meet Sunita before getting married to her. However, complications arise when Jai falls in love with Kimi, while on his way to Sunita's village.

title: Hum Hain Rahi Pyar Ke
subTitle: Rahul looks after his spoilt nephews, Sunny and Vicky, and niece, Munni. When they go to a funfair, they meet Vyjayanti, who has run away from home, and decide to shelter her without Rahul's consent.

title: Bewaffa Se Waffa
subTitle: Rukhsar asks her best friend Nagma to marry her husband, Aslam, and mother a child for him when she is unable to do it herself. However, problems begin when Nagma's relatives cause discord among them.

title: Jigariyaa
subTitle: Shaamu, who lives a carefree life, falls in love with a well-educated girl, Raadha. However, circumstances force the young couple to part ways.

title: J.D.
subTitle: JD, an ambitious journalist known for integrity, spirals into addiction and scandal. Subsequently, his career and reputation crumble when he's accused of raping a colleague who works for him.

title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.

title: Lootere
subTitle: Police inspectors Karan and Ali investigate the murder of a colleague, Inspector Rane. Karan takes the responsibility of protecting Anjali, a bar dancer who is a key witness to the crime.

title: Lootere
subTitle: Police inspectors Karan and Ali investigate the murder of a colleague, Inspector Rane. Karan takes the responsibility of protecting Anjali, a bar dancer who is a key witness to the crime.

title: Waqt Hamara Hai
subTitle: Friends Vikas and Sunil, along with their girlfriends, Ayesha and Mamta, unknowingly become a part of an awful terrorist plot to kill a minister.

title: I M 24
subTitle: A 42-year-old writer falls in love with a 22-year-old beauty queen. However, things get complicated when his roommate encourages him to make up stories to impress her.

title: Maine Dil Tujhko Diya
subTitle: Ajay falls in love with Ayesha, a fellow college student who is the daughter of a rich businessman. However, problems arise when Ayesha's father arranges her marriage to an associate's son.

title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Jab Pyaar Kisise Hota Hai
subTitle: Sooraj Dhanrajgir, a playboy, falls in love with Komal, who rejects him because of his vices and gives him time to change. Things go awry when a little boy shows up claiming to be his son.

title: Dil Pardesi Ho Gayaa
subTitle: When Major Ram of the Indian Army is captured by the Pakistani military, his younger brother Sunny begins a daring mission to rescue him, only to find himself falling for a Pakistani woman.

title: Mohabbat
subTitle: When Shekhar falls for Roopa, he approaches her father with his parents. However, when his stepmother asks Roopa's father for dowry, he vows to marry his daughter elsewhere.

title: Saath Saath
subTitle: Gita, a girl from a wealthy family, falls in love with an idealistic Avinash who has stern principles in life. However, his changed behaviour post marriage troubles her.

title: Doli Saja Ke Rakhna
subTitle: Inder and Pallavi fall for each other but her three possessive brothers hate him. Resultantly, the couple elopes but they soon find themselves missing their families and decide to return.

title: Har Dil Jo Pyar Karega
subTitle: Raj, an aspiring singer, rescues Pooja, the daughter of a wealthy man, from an accident. However, he soon finds himself in a web of complications when he falls in love with her best friend.
